com.upsight.android.analytics.internal

Class DataStoreRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.upsight.android.analytics.internal.DataStoreRecord

  • public final class DataStoreRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a record of insertion, update or removal of an object in the data store. All of the three operations generate a record which the Upsight dispatcher can communicate to the server in order to process the data in the analytics pipeline.
